☐ Api Routes :
    ☐ GET       /api/home                   Returns a list of recent or popular questions.
    ☐ POST      /api/login                  Authenticates a user with their username and password.
    ☐ POST      /api/signup                 Creates a new user account with the provided information.
    ☐ GET       /api/questions              Returns a list of all questions.
    ☐ GET       /api/questions/[id]         Returns details of a specific question with the given ID.
    ☐ POST      /api/questions              Creates a new question with the provided information.
    ☐ PUT       /api/questions/[id]         Updates a specific question with the given ID.
    ☐ DELETE    /api/questions/[id]         Deletes a specific question with the given ID.
    ☐ GET       /api/search?q=[query]       Searches for questions that match the given query.
    ☐ POST      /api/answers                Adds a new answer to a specific question.
    ☐ PUT       /api/answers/[id]           Updates a specific answer with the given ID.
    ☐ DELETE    /api/answers/[id]           Deletes a specific answer with the given ID.

☐ DB Structure :
    ☐ Users
        ☐ id (primary key)
        ☐ username
        ☐ email
        ☐ password
    ☐ Questions
        ☐ id (primary key)
        ☐ title
        ☐ body
        ☐ user_id (foreign key referencing Users.id)
        ☐ created_at
        ☐ updated_at
    ☐ Answers
        ☐ id (primary key)
        ☐ body
        ☐ user_id (foreign key referencing Users.id)
        ☐ question_id (foreign key referencing Questions.id)
        ☐ created_at
        ☐ updated_at
